title: Marina Cove wants YOU to become a resident here at this community!
posting_body: ['Apt #355 could be your new place to call home just in time for Spring! 🦋🌷🌞', 'Black/Stainless steel appliances, in-unit washer and dryer, quartz counter tops, courtyard view and hardwood-like flooring!', 'Lease 2b 2ba apartment #355', 'Priced at $3164 for an 13-month lease', 'Each of our garden-style apartment homes for rent is finished in modern style with quartz countertops, a combination of hardwood-style vinyl flooring and carpet, and sleek, streamlined finishes.', 'Additional conveniences include air conditioning, spacious storage closets, a washer and dryer, and your own private patio or balcony to enjoy the fresh air.', 'With 1- and 2-bedroom floor plans in a variety of layouts, we’re sure to have the right one for you.', '30-Day Satisfaction Guarantee ✨', 'If you are not 100% satisfied with your home, you may transfer to a comparable residence within the community or terminate your lease.', 'Some restrictions may apply.', 'do NOT contact me with unsolicited services or offers', 'Marina Cove Apartments', '3480 Granada Avenue.', 'Santa Clara, CA 95051', 'show contact info', 'https://essexapts.info/Marina-Cove']
